    "description": "将完整版加入愿望清单<br>更多角色、武器、技能等着您！<br><br><br>Beautiful Mystic Survivors是一款roguelite动作游戏，你将协助花颜月貌的美少女们击退排山倒海的怪物，在这过程中需要思考战略技巧，让她们升级得以屠杀敌人，当然，你的「奖励」是绝对少不了的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149790/extras/9e7b2c6debb7381efb947321f7a2a038.avif?t=1724996646\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149790/extras/f3ebac9f21a2c23ccc931bc2e02f8f35.poster.avif?t=1724996646\" width=620 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149790/extras/f3ebac9f21a2c23ccc931bc2e02f8f35.webm?t=1724996646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>战火纷飞，前线的捍卫者是一群千娇百媚的可爱女孩子，无私地以自己的肉身阻挡敌人，守护着这个世界，然而众寡悬殊，就在战线濒临崩溃时－－你出现了，故事就此展开！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149790/extras/f25fb6ebdc3de0e2a94f402292c3d8ca.avif?t=1724996646\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149790/extras/ac2ad034a9986f90af08117c2026bd25.poster.avif?t=1724996646\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149790/extras/ac2ad034a9986f90af08117c2026bd25.webm?t=1724996646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149790/extras/ac2ad034a9986f90af08117c2026bd25.mp4?t=1724996646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>&quot;时限之内把敌人消灭吧－－在这个反转的弹幕游戏裡，换你用弹幕来割草！<br>多种可解锁角色任君挑选，她们各有特殊能力，搭配不同武器和遗物，让你玩出自己的风格。<br>随机生成的地图，每次战斗都是满满的新鲜感～♪&quot;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=